  a query:

  ```csharp
  using MongoDB.Bson;
  using MyCompany.Embeddings;

  var aiService = new AIService();
  var queryString = "ocean tragedy";
  var queryEmbedding = await aiService.GetEmbeddingsAsync([queryString]);

  if (!queryEmbedding.Any())
